How to start the gui:

1. Run com.sones.main.Main
2. Login if you have account, or create a new account and try to login.
3. If the login process succeed, then you move in a form from which you can start the downloader.


Get your token:

1. Click on token button
2. Click on get request
3. Paste the request into a browser
4. Login on facebook
5. Copy the access token that it returned to the browser into the edit box
6. Click on save button

Select sources

1. Click on sources
2. Download your friend list if you haven't already
3. Load your friend list
4. Double click the sources you want.
5. Save

Downloader

1. Click on downloader button
2. On Settings > Interval give the interval in milliseconds.
3. Start downloading